snippet.title: Defenders of the Omniverse Demo Teaser
snippet.description:
Defenders of the Omniverse is a Reverse Bullet Hell Rogue-Lite set in a world between realities, where heroes and monsters from all across space and time face off in the final battle for the fate of the Omniverse!

Wishlist the game! https://store.steampowered.com/app/2461840/Defenders_of_the_Omniverse/
Join Discord: https://discord.com/invite/dgtPYxvjgt
Twitter: https://twitter.com/BabushkaEnt
